{"about_the_game":"In Aery - Broken Memories you enter the mind of another person in order to bring them back from a coma.<br>\u200b<br>Within the other human's mind, you are represented through a little bird that moves smoothly through thoughts, fears, and memories.<br>\u200b<br>Your objective is to find memory shards in order to get to know the other person, to progress with the story, and to unlock new, unknown areas of the mind.<br>\u200b<br>Experience the feeling of flying, immerse into beautiful and atmospheric landscapes and enjoy the unique storytelling of the game while getting to know a new friend on the fly.<br><br>What else? <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Experience the feeling of flying with fluid and responsive flight controls<br></li><li> See the world with the eyes of a bird with intuitive and relaxing gameplay<br></li><li> Experience the speed of a bird without enemies or other threats<br></li><li> Explore 15 vast landscapes with a different theme, style, and mood<br></li><li> Follow the cute story of a little bird<br></li><li> Collect the feathers of other birds to unlock the next area<br></li><li> Immerse into the atmosphere with a vibrant minimalistic yet sometimes even surreal art style<br></li><li> Enjoy the beautiful bright colors with interesting and different color themes in every area<br></li><li> Discover hidden areas and many little surprises on your way</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"World I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1424790/86cb86df7f7de4398744339d5845b0ad0bb8b7a0.jpg"},{"name":"World II","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1424790/86cb86df7f7de4398744339d5845b0ad0bb8b7a0.jpg"},{"name":"World III","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1424790/86cb86df7f7de4398744339d5845b0ad0bb8b7a0.jpg"},{"name":"World IV","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/142479